- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is also likely as the paper discusses numerical method developments and performance improvements.
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is another possible category as the paper describes the application of the framework to various engineering problems.
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is a possible category as the paper discusses strategies for parallel I/O and exploiting hardware.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also possible as the paper describes software and performance developments.
